# 文件功能：忽略平台仓库在本地开发、构建、调试过程中产生的临时文件、依赖目录、环境变量文件与构建产物。

# OS / Editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
*.log
logs/
.codex-run-logs/
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Tool caches
.codex/
.cache/

# Environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyd
*.so
.python-version
.venv/
venv/
env/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/

# Node.js / Frontend
node_modules/
.pnpm-store/
.npm/
dist/
.vite/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo
playwright-report/
test-results/

# Backend artifacts
backend/build_artifacts/
backend/data/
backend/output.txt
backend/test_output.txt
backend/test_result.txt

# Temporary files
tmp/
temp/
.tmp/
*.tmp
